                <note rend="inline" type="source">662.6331/277: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in the Netherlands</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The Hague</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-09-05T11:00:00+01:19"
                            >September 5, 1931—11 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received September 5—6:38 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>29. My telegram No. 28, September 3, 10 a.m.<note n="24" xml:id="d446fn24">Not
                        printed.</note> Court decides by eight votes to seven Customs Union not
                    compatible with Geneva Protocol.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
